deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Wednesday, February 21 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35
features: Declutters entryways by housing up to 8 pairs of shoes
Rustic gray wooden finish imbues a natural aesthetic
Slim profile tucks neatly into a hallway or closet
Slatted shelves for better air circulation and fresher footwear
Easy to assemble; no tools needed
body.description: This shoe rack is the perfect storage solution for a busy entryway door. If there’s a lot of traffic or if space is tight on your way in the door, this 2-tier wooden shoe rack is the ideal place to plop a handbag and kick off a pair of boots. This isn’t a command center—the place where an entire collection of footwear can be proudly displayed (though we sell those too!). Think of this shoe rack as more a temporary home for a child’s backpack right after school, or a quick resting place for winter boots as they dry from a snowy jaunt outdoors. The rack’s slim wooden profile would also make it an easy addition to any closet, quickly doubling its shoe storage capacity.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for small spaces
reviews.reviewText: It currently holds most of the shoes in my room and fits perfectly under the thing I wanted it to fit under.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I actually eeally like this shoe rack. You get what you pay for. I think it looks good. Easy to put together and despite what other reviews say, if you know how to use a screw driver, you don’t need glue to hold it together. 10/10

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Very cheaply made
reviews.reviewText: I will keep this product because it was inexpensive and will serve my purposes. It is described as “rustic”, but I would describe it as poorly and cheaply constructed. Since it will be in the closet, no one else will see it. That is good because it is not pretty.

reviews.reviewText: I love it but it’s not very study as it has no screws or anything to keep it together jus fits down inside itself if u have any type of wood glue use it!
